FTPFXP Ruby Gem
===============

Author: Lee, Alex
License: Ruby License
E-mail: alexeen@gmail.com
Home Page: http://ftpfxp.rubyforge.org/
Project Page: http://rubyforge.org/projects/ftpfxp

The purpose of this project is to extend the standard Net::FTP
module by providing Server-to-Server file transfer and SSL/TLS
secure control and data connection capabilities. SSL/TLS support
for file transfer using SSCN and CPSV are both supported.

Sample codes are under `./samples/'

For information on the license, read `LICENSE.txt'.

Copyright (C)2006, Alex Lee. All Rights Reserved.
